          {
            "commit": "65c09e8f1bea72e1fbeffd31cef7334c4b094050",
            "subject": "LU-3270 statahead: statahead thread wait for RPCs to finish"
          }
        ],
        "author": {
          "name": "Lai Siyao",
          "email": "lai.siyao@intel.com",
          "date": "2014-03-12 03:07:09.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Lai Siyao",
          "email": "lai.siyao@intel.com",
          "date": "2014-09-19 10:38:27.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3270 statahead: use dcache-like interface for sa entry",
        "message": "LU-3270 statahead: use dcache-like interface for sa entry\n\nRename ll_sa_entry to sa_entry, and manage sa_entry cache with\ndcache-like interfaces.\n\nsa_entry is not needed to be refcounted, because only scanner\ncan free it, so after it's put in stat list, statahead thread\nshouldn't access it any longer.\n\nll_statahead_interpret() doesn't need to take sai refcount,\nbecause statahead thread will wait for all inflight RPC to\nfinish.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I0633ffbb0e97982c58976ea696c0784ce2d1ce01\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_4"
    }
  },
